other_tests.findings: Normal activity of the classical, MBL, and alternative complement pathways.
Low response to pneumococcal polysaccharide vaccine; normal responses to H. influenzae type b, diphtheria, and tetanus vaccines.
No detectable levels of ficolin-3 in the homozygous patient; median concentration in heterozygous patients was 14.1 Î¼g/mL.
No C4 deposition in the patient's serum; normal C4 deposition observed when serum was reconstituted with recombinant ficolin-3.
